Introduction

YPDA (Korean: 예쁘다; Japanese: かわいい) was a duo under J Company Entertainment. They originally debuted as a four member girl group on June 1, 2018, with the mini-album 예뻐지다. Their last activity was around October 2019, hinting that they might’ve disbanded then. On March 10, 2021 Sungbin made an instagram post on the duo's instagram page but no updates have been provided since then. With the closing of the company and no updates from the last two members since then it's safe to assume the duo is officially disbanded.
